{"tid":1660744,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"用資訊爆炸去隱藏資訊","createTime":"2019-10-17T16:29:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T16:43:53.000Z","uid":321588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"aa7bed870dc8b97f39deafb1f2e4a5ff1fdcebb9","tid":1660744,"uid":321588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T16:29:21.000Z","msg":"如果做左D野但唔想俾人知可以點做?<br />\n最好既當然係收收埋埋唔俾人發現,<br />\n但係要一D蛛絲馬跡都唔留係好難既,<br />\n俾人發現左可以點做?<br />\n<br />\nA公司同B公司係死對頭,<br />\n而A公司搵左係B公司做既C君做商業間諜,<br />\n因為有C君既幫手A公司好多事情上都比B公司捷足先登,<br />\nB公司發現有異常開始內部調查,<br />\n呢個時候A公司放出大量謠言,<br />\n例如係B公司做既鍾意炒股既D君炒股炒燶左要一筆錢填數,<br />\n平時十分吝嗇既E君好似有左一大筆錢突然變得闊綽,<br />\n花錢沒節制既F俾財務公司追得好緊,<br />\n睇下邊個謠言比較吸引B公司注意力,<br />\n再係謠言上放D模稜兩可既消息,<br />\n某某係邊日去過邊間餐廳,而A公司既某經理個日都有去個間餐廳,<br />\n係B公司俾謠言牽著走期間,<br />\nC君得到左消除同A公司接觸時留低蛛絲馬跡既時間<br />\n<br />\n本人都幾陰謀論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到連登最近既貼有感而發"},{"pid":"5c582534c022cf064d77872a3a50f3593397d6d3","tid":1660744,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T16:29:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Yk6szE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Yk6szE.jpg&h=f0e63ff5&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3cd9956b9a69ee5941dffd1799800d05467c08c3","tid":1660744,"uid":38494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T16:43:53.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人</span>反抗</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">WE SHALL NEVER SURRENDER</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VCmRc9t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVCmRc9t.jpg&h=8c479605&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x1oPKga.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx1oPKga.jpg&h=3606b343&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"}]}